# https://swagger.io/docs/specification/using-ref/
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: JSON Schemas test spec
  license:
    name: MIT
paths:
  /things:
    x-vertx-event-bus:
     address: test.admin
     timeout: 1000

    get:
      operationId: getThings
      responses:
        default:
          description: "OK"
      parameters:
        - $ref: "#/components/parameters/ParamQ_FilterByString" 

components:
  
  parameters:

    ParamQ_FilterByString:
      in: query
      name: filter
      required: false
      schema:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/FilterPredicates"

  schemas:
           
    FilterPredicates:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/FilterPredicate"            
      
    FilterPredicate:
      type: object
      properties:
        field:
          type: string
        operator:
          type: string
        value:
          type: string
      title: filter_predicate

Error: make ir: path "/things": get: parameters: nested objects not allowed
